acks are fetched"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"from the database. After that point, this property is always non-nil, but it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"may be empty to indicate that no packs are present."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To detect when the shared offline storage object has finished loading its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property, observe KVO change notifications on the "},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" key path."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The initial load results in an "},{"code":"NSKeyValueChangeSetting","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" change."}]}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","title":"MLNOfflineStorage","role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflineStorage"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data so